In re Resignation of Moore.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Moore (1989), 45 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. 89-1397 Submitted August 15, 1989 Decided September 13, 1989.)

The resignation of William Julius Moore as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
